    • HANDLE_BASE

      static final int HANDLE_BASE
      The base value for all CONSTANT_MethodHandle constant pool items. Internally, there are 9 variations of CONSTANT_MethodHandle items, which are stored into 9 different items, of types 21 to 29.
      See Also:
      • Constant Field Values

    • BSM

      static final int BSM
      The type of BootstrapMethod items. These items are stored in a special class attribute named "BootstrapMethods" and not in the constant pool.
